# Mule Account Investigation Runbook

## Review Steps

1. Start with high and critical alerts, then open the linked account concept.
2. Compare triggered signals with the evidence table and configured thresholds.
3. Review cluster links to understand bounded account-to-account context.
4. Check aggregate values against approved source systems before any action.
5. Record analyst disposition outside regenerated pipeline artifacts.

This runbook supports human review. It does not confirm fraud.

